Package com.codisimus.plugins.phatloots.listeners

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CitizensListener
    Listens for NPC Spawns/Deaths and checks if there is a PhatLoot named after them
    DispenserListener
    Listens for redstone activating PhatLoot Dispensers
    FishingListener
    Listens for Fishing events and handles what is caught
    LootBagListener
    Listens for interactions with Loot bags
    MobDeathListener
    Manages Mob drops when Mobs die
    MobListener
    Listens for Mob events that trigger loots
    MobSpawnListener
    Listens for Mob spawning to equip them with armor and a weapon
    PhatLootsListener
    Listens for interactions with PhatLootChests
    VoteListener
    Listens for Votes triggered by Votifier and gives the Voter Loot
